{"tid":1652931,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[我唔係左膠]不如下次再遇到藍絲/休班狗綁係條燈柱到","createTime":"2019-10-14T01:06:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T08:30:31.000Z","uid":8740,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"07c755bfc06c3471f4fa87bdafa815e1ab077f6a","tid":1652931,"uid":8740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T01:06:23.000Z","msg":"出神獸又比左膠阻撚住<br />\n出手既手足又可能比黑警追究<br />\n橫掂D狗又咁鍾意玩綑綁<br />\n不如下次遇到就將佢地綁起係條燈柱到<br />\n每年同日就po出黎侮辱下佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等佢地d子子孫孫都見到佢地既柒事<br />\n<br />\n咁做就可以比外國傳媒見到我地已經止暴<br />\n受害者冇見紅又唔會有人可憐佢地<br />\n<br />\nD黃家長好似我老母個d成日都叫我唔好打趕佢走就算<br />\n因為始終老一輩既都有一顆憐憫之心<br />\n我覺得綁起黎羞辱佢地係一個唔錯既做法"},{"pid":"d059572ecf5f9ac770a8cc5c3ee7e0d972439ffa","tid":1652931,"uid":296520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T01:07:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AtofU5z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAtofU5z.jpg&h=17e95e86&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4333ac5b1153f6018ad4ac378eb4dbc50d1abfad","tid":1652931,"uid":222896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T01:15:26.000Z","msg":"CLS"},{"pid":"a3c2f21d7136fdc20cc53894099ba34d21700c83","tid":1652931,"uid":320676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T01:19:45.000Z","msg":"綁上去阻膠就無得救佢，等左膠行開啲就可以處理佢"},{"pid":"8ef676236256dff33d821324832d21a090a157f9","tid":1652931,"uid":8740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T01:32:37.000Z","msg":"綁住等記者影相<br />\n唔好比左膠救佢"},{"pid":"5c7835f600194ea20c2afe033e849026e13a65ff","tid":1652931,"uid":8740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T01:44:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"46b2dfd8fb6e75f0b636490fa8e5b8504146b858","tid":1652931,"uid":8740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:02:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f942970526988ff1ec9bf1be029b19ce46cbb252","tid":1652931,"uid":34553,"